  = waypoint action="sectionDidChange" sectionName="services" classNames="services section"
    .small-12.columns
      h1.austincyr-fat.animated.fadeInDown.padding-bottom Our Services
      .row
        .small-12.large-4.columns
          img.animated.bounceIn.padding-bottom src="./assets/images/pencil.png"
          h3.brown-regular.padding-bottom Web Design
          h4.brown-light.padding-bottom This ain't our first rodeo.  To us, bad UX stands out like a sore thumb, and yes, we're know that your content is king.
        .small-12.large-4.columns
          img.animated.bounceIn.padding-bottom src="./assets/images/code.png"
          h3.brown-regular.padding-bottom Development
          h4.brown-light.padding-bottom We're expert coders.  We believe in shared solutions - and love reusing code!  That's why we're an Ember / Rails shop.
        .small-12.large-4.columns
          img.animated.bounceIn.padding-bottom src="./assets/images/man.png"
          h3.brown-regular.padding-bottom Consulting
          h4.brown-light.padding-bottom Want to get your team up to speed with Ember or Rails quick?  We also do consulting, and pair programming.  Catch us at the NYC Ember meetups!

